.SH Status
\fBjava.lang.Math\fR, \fBjava.lang.System\fR, \fBjava.lang.Integer\fR,
\fBjava.lang.Long\fR, \fBjava.lang.String\fR, \fBjava.lang.Double\fR,
\fBjava.lang.Boolean\fR, \fBjava.lang.Character\fR, \fBjava.lang.Thread\fR
(\fBsleep\fR only), \fBjava.util.regex.Pattern\fR (with Matcher),
\fBjava.util.UUID\fR, and \fBjava.time.Instant\fR are usable. \fBjava.lang.Class\fR,
\fBjava.io.File\fR, \fBjava.lang.Throwable\fR, and other commonly-used classes
are on the roadmap and will follow the same three-layer pattern.
